ddns-updater (1.2.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enforce persistent storage in /var/lib/ddns-updater only
  * Remove /tmp fallback to prevent data loss across reboots
  * Enhanced installation script creates storage directory automatically
  * Updated systemd service files for persistent storage only
  * Added comprehensive persistent storage documentation
  * Improved error handling for storage accessibility issues
  * Better data persistence and system reliability

 -- DDNS Updater Team <dev@example.com>  Thu, 03 Oct 2025 12:00:00 +0000

ddns-updater (1.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enhanced JSON storage with full absolute path logging
  * Improved debugging output showing complete file paths
  * Smart JSON file creation and IP presence checking
  * Non-intrusive updates (only modify existing entries)
  * Enhanced Apache configuration support
  * Better backup management (only create backups when IP changes)
  * Comprehensive logging improvements for troubleshooting

 -- GitHub Actions <action@github.com>  Thu, 03 Oct 2025 10:30:00 +0000

